      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone prioritizing utility over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some minor dings on the passenger side, and clear coat thinning on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has visible wear and a few small stains, though all essential electronics and climate controls remain functional. It has been maintained regularly to ensure it runs reliably, making it a solid choice for someone needing honest transportation at a reasonable price.",
