    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This FD3S Mazda RX-7 retains its iconic 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary powerplant, delivering a linear power band and exceptional throttle response. The chassis remains rigid, featuring the original four-wheel double-wishbone suspension geometry and a Torsen limited-slip differential for precise cornering kinematics. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive vacuum line refresh and an inspection of the apex seals to ensure optimal compression across both rotors. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals are robust, with the cooling system upgraded to a high-capacity aluminum radiator to mitigate heat soak. A purist\u2019s example ready for the track or spirited canyon runs.",
